| **Word**     | **What LSTM Does**                                                                          |
| ------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| I            | Stores subject information.                                                                 |
| love         | Stores the relationship with the subject.                                                   |
| learning     | Continues updating the memory.                                                              |
| Artificial   | Recognizes it as part of a phrase.                                                          |
| Intelligence | Combines with "Artificial" to understand **Artificial Intelligence** as a complete concept. |


